adqlQueryList: SELECT funnel(segments.httpData.sessionId, segments.userData.UserStep = "Authenticate" AND segments.userData.Version = "version_2.0", segments.userData.UserStep = "Account Profile", segments.userData.UserStep = "Offers", segments.userData.UserStep = "Convert Offer") AS "Authenticate,Account Profile,Receive Offer,Convert Offer" FROM transactions WHERE application = "AD-DevOps"

SELECT funnel(segments.httpData.sessionId, segments.userData.UserStep = "Authenticate" AND segments.userData.Version = "version_1.0", segments.userData.UserStep = "Account Profile", segments.userData.UserStep = "Offers", segments.userData.UserStep = "Convert Offer") AS "Authenticate,Account Profile,Receive Offer,Convert Offer" FROM transactions WHERE application = "AD-DevOps"
SELECT distinctcount(segments.httpData.sessionId) AS " " FROM transactions WHERE segments.userData.Version = "version_2.0"
SELECT distinctcount(segments.httpData.sessionId) AS " " FROM transactions WHERE segments.userData.Version = "version_1.0"

SELECT ((filter(count(*), where segments.userData.UserStep = "Convert Offer") * 1.0) /  (filter(count(*), where segments.userData.UserStep = "Authenticate"))) * 100 AS " " FROM transactions WHERE segments.userData.Version = "version_2.0"
SELECT sum(segments.userData.`Offer-Converted-Value`) AS " " FROM transactions WHERE segments.userData.UserStep = "Convert Offer" and segments.userData.Version = "version_2.0"
SELECT series(eventTimestamp, '10m'), segments.userData.Version AS Version, percentile(responseTime, 90) AS "Resp. Time 90%" FROM transactions LIMIT 2000
SELECT segments.userData.Version AS "Version" FROM transactions LIMIT 10

SELECT ((filter(count(*), where segments.userData.UserStep = "Convert Offer") * 1.0) /  (filter(count(*), where segments.userData.UserStep = "Authenticate"))) * 100 AS " " FROM transactions WHERE segments.userData.Version = "version_1.0"
SELECT sum(segments.userData.`Offer-Converted-Value`) AS " " FROM transactions WHERE segments.userData.UserStep = "Convert Offer" and segments.userData.Version = "version_1.0"
